{"tid":116471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉趁16歲女酒醉性交　浸大毅進生被控強姦","createTime":"2017-02-11T12:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T04:15:15.000Z","uid":51512,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f97084f9a0fca37322c3dc87ee6b60cb0627e605","tid":116471,"uid":51512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"在浸會大學就讀毅進課程的18歲李景新，被指於上月底與16歲女友人行花市後在住所飲酒，涉嫌在對方飲醉後與其性交，被控一項強姦罪，今在沙田法院提堂。他暫毋須答辯，案件押後至3月27日在粉嶺法院再訊，期間被告還押。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告於本年1月27日，在上水住所強姦女子X。<br />\n<br />\n控方指，事主16歲，透過朋友介紹認識被告。兩人案發前相約行花市，但被告之後提議改到其住所飲啤酒，事主同意，惟事主飲醉後，在不情願下和被告性交。辯方提出以15萬元申請擔保，但遭裁判官拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170211/bkn-20170211133717436-0211_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170211%2Fbkn-20170211133717436-0211_00822_001.html&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c4397196\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170211/bkn-20170211133717436-0211_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8d4fa42b9d7b684bbca7e4f3c959abe1c3416265","tid":116471,"uid":10313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:29:05.000Z","msg":"18歲仔拎得出15萬<br />\n<br />\n早啲俾就冇事啦傻仔"},{"pid":"7d4ff27688688734dd5cd1db8f0995e15b2725af","tid":116471,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"1e0c682ec028a0e9ac8a310e4d83c184031de243","tid":116471,"uid":35857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"15萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如屌我吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a629e1cd57745a40288f4c940361a8baa88e71ea","tid":116471,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>15萬<img src=\"/asset